    'No heavy works or demolition',
    'Minimal debris and dust',
    '3-4× faster install than brick',
    'Integrated services inside the wall',
    'Built-in acoustic and thermal insulation',
    'Compatible with historic buildings',
    'Perfectly smooth surface for painting',
    '1-year warranty on labour',
  ],
  aniosTitle: 'Renovations in Menorca since 2004',
  aniosText: 'Since 2004 our SL matriz has completed over 6,000 drywall renovation projects across the Balearic Islands. We know the buildings, the local regulations and the specific challenges of Menorcan construction.',
  aniosStars: '4.7/5 on Google',
  tiposEyebrow: 'Complete solutions',
  tiposH2: 'Types of interior drywall renovations',
  tiposLead: 'The four drywall solutions most requested in Menorca: layout redistribution with partitions (from €45/m²), false ceilings (from €29/m²), acoustic insulation (from €6/m² in materials) and thermal wall linings (from €7/m²). Here is when to use each.',
  tiposReformas: [
    {
      num: '01',
      titulo: 'Space redistribution with drywall partitions',
      parrafos: [
        'Layout redistribution with drywall partitions from €45/m² is the most common renovation in Menorca, especially in Maó city-centre flats built before 1980 with outdated layouts: oversized lounges, bedrooms without ventilation, corridors that steal 4-6 m² of usable area, or studios that need to become two bedrooms.',
        'We design and deliver any floorplan redistribution in 3-7 days. The galvanised steel frame is anchored to floor and ceiling without any masonry, and Placo/Knauf plasterboard is screwed onto it for a smooth finish ready to paint 24 hours later. The partition cavity (70 mm) houses electrical wiring, HVAC piping and ducts.',
        'A standard partition is just 10 cm thick in total (12.5 mm board + M70 stud + 12.5 mm board), recovering 5-8% more usable floor area compared with 15 cm brick. With 45 mm Knauf/Isover mineral wool inside, it reaches 45-50 dB DnT,A of acoustic insulation without any increase in thickness.',
        'Drywall partitions are also ideal for built-in wardrobes, dry-sided bathrooms, home-office zones and children’s bedrooms. They accept curves, angles and organic shapes with flexible Placo Glasroc F board — geometries that would double the cost in brick.',
      ],
      linkTexto: 'See all drywall partition types',
      linkHref: '/en/tabiques-pladur-menorca',
    },
    {
      num: '02',
      titulo: 'Drywall false ceilings to modernise any space',
      parrafos: [
        'Drywall false ceilings in Menorca start from €29/m² and are one of the most impactful transformations a home can undergo. In Menorcan 20th-century flats with 3-4 m ceilings, a false ceiling drops the height to 2.4-2.7 m, creates warmer ambiences, integrates recessed LED lighting and conceals heating pipes, exposed wiring or deteriorated beams without any chasing or demolition.',
        'The seamless smooth ceiling (€29-35/m²) is the most common in homes: a flat surface dropped 10-20 cm from the original, with integrated recessed LED downlights (€45-80/unit), HVAC diffusers and speakers. Coffered, stepped or decorative ceilings rise to €45-80/m² and deliver the volume effects highly prized in design renovations.',
        'In shops, hotels and restaurants in Menorca, false ceilings segment zones, improve acoustics and accept paint, vinyl and any decorative finish. For venues required to meet CTE DB-SI (public-use premises, holiday flats, hotels), we offer <a href="/en/pladur-ignifugo-menorca" class="text-foreground font-semibold underline underline-offset-2">certified EI-60 and EI-120 fire-rated drywall</a> from €52/m².',
        'A key Menorca detail: we coordinate grille and diffuser placement with the HVAC installer before closing the ceiling, avoiding the typical "bumps" or later patches. In holiday flats with ducted or cassette AC, this coordination saves €300-600 per unit in rework.',
      ],
      linkTexto: 'See all drywall false ceiling types',
      linkHref: '/en/falsos-techos-pladur-menorca',
    },
    {
      num: '03',
      titulo: 'Acoustic insulation between neighbours with drywall systems',
      parrafos: [
        'Acoustic insulation with drywall in Menorca costs from €6/m² (material) and solves one of the biggest issues of flat living. Maó, Ciutadella and other tourist municipalities have dense urban fabrics; the acoustic standards of buildings built between 1960 and 1990 are 10-15 dB below what the CTE DB-HR now requires (DnT,A ≥ 50 dBA between dwellings).',
        'Drywall soundproofing systems combine three techniques: double BA15 acoustic board on one or both partition faces, high-density mineral wool (60-80 kg/m³) in the cavity, and a decoupled frame with Placo/Knauf anti-vibration bands that block flanking transmission through the building structure.',
        'A standard drywall partition with mineral wool reaches 45-50 dB DnT,A, meeting the CTE-HR minimum between bedrooms. Premium solutions with double BA15 board and decoupled frame exceed 55 dB, making the room effectively soundproofed. For recording studios, rehearsal rooms and home cinemas we offer box-in-box systems from €150/m² with over 65 dB certified reduction.',
        'This solution is heavily in demand from holiday-flat owners seeking to improve their Airbnb/Booking scores (a 0.5-point increase in "noise" raises occupancy by 8-12%) and from homes next to hospitality venues affected by night-time noise.',
      ],
      linkTexto: 'See acoustic insulation solutions in Menorca',
      linkHref: '/en/aislamiento-acustico-menorca',
    },
    {
      num: '04',
      titulo: 'Thermal upgrade with drywall wall linings',
      parrafos: [
        'A drywall wall lining from €29/m² improves the thermal performance of facades, party walls and walls in contact with the outside. It adds a second drywall face over the existing wall with a 40-80 mm cavity filled with insulation: Isover mineral wool (€7-12/m²), XPS extruded polystyrene (€10-15/m²) or sprayed polyurethane foam (€12-18/m²).',
        'In the Mediterranean climate of Menorca (climate zone B3 per CTE-HE, summers of 30-34 °C with high summer humidity), a thermal wall lining cuts AC consumption by 20-35%. In an 80 m² home with a €1,800 annual electric bill, the estimated saving is €360-630/year. Typical payback sits between 5 and 10 years depending on prior consumption and existing envelope.',
        'A wall lining also improves the energy rating: moving from an E rating to a C raises the property value by 5-15% in the Balearic market, according to studies by the Balearic APIs property agents association. A decisive factor in a market where 60% of foreign buyers require a C-or-above energy certificate.',
      ],
      linkTexto: 'See drywall thermal insulation solutions',
      linkHref: '/en/aislamiento-termico-menorca',
    },
  ],
  compEyebrow: 'Technical comparison',
  compH2: 'Drywall vs traditional build in interior renovations',
  compLead: 'An objective comparison of the two systems to help you make the right choice for your project.',
  compPladur: 'Drywall',
  compTrad: 'Traditional build',
  comparativa: [
    { criterio: 'Build time', pladur: '1-2 weeks for a full flat', obraTradicional: '4-8 weeks including curing and drying' },
    { criterio: 'Debris generated', pladur: 'Minimal — no wall chasing or demolition', obraTradicional: 'High — debris bags, dust, noise' },
    { criterio: 'Indicative price', pladur: 'From €45/m² (complete partition)', obraTradicional: 'From €55/m² (hollow brick + plaster)' },
    { criterio: 'Final result', pladur: 'Perfectly smooth surface, ready to paint', obraTradicional: 'Needs additional plaster and more time' },
    { criterio: 'Integrated services', pladur: 'Electrical, plumbing and HVAC inside', obraTradicional: 'Requires wall chasing and cutting' },
    { criterio: 'Structural weight', pladur: 'Very light — no load added to the slab', obraTradicional: 'Adds significant load to the building' },
    { criterio: 'Impact on occupied home', pladur: 'You can live in the home during the work', obraTradicional: 'Usually requires vacating the home' },
  ],
  normQuote: '"The Spanish Technical Building Code requires vertical separation elements between different use units to achieve an airborne sound insulation DnT,A of at least 50 dB in residential use, ensuring protection against noise between dwellings and between dwellings and common areas."',
  normQuoteCite: '— CTE DB-HR, Basic Document on Protection against Noise, Table 2.1',
  preciosEyebrow: 'Renovation prices',
  preciosH2: 'How much does an interior drywall renovation cost in Menorca?',
  preciosP1: 'An interior drywall renovation in Menorca costs between €10,000 and €20,000 for an 80-100 m² flat (full false ceiling + redistribution + basic insulation). The exact price depends on job type, square metres, complexity and chosen Placo/Knauf materials. These are the indicative 2026 prices by line item:',
  preciosP2: 'Basic layout partition (BA13 board per side, no insulation): €45-52/m². Partition with mineral wool acoustic insulation: €52-58/m². Seamless BA13 false ceiling: €29-35/m². False ceiling with integrated LED lighting: €35-47/m² depending on the number of points. Thermal wall lining on facade: €35-48/m². All prices exclude VAT.',
  preciosP3: 'Prices in Menorca run 10-15% above the mainland average due to sea freight of materials from the manufacturers (Placo-Saint-Gobain in Valdemoro, Knauf in Guixers) and Balearic wage pressure. Even so, drywall is 25-40% cheaper than brick once you count labour (3-4× slower), time (4-8 weeks vs 1-2) and debris management (skip vs manual removal).',
  preciosP4: 'For a full flat renovation (false ceiling + complete redistribution + basic insulation), typical budgets for an 80-100 m² flat in Menorca range from €10,000 to €20,000 depending on finish level. A turn-key renovation for holiday-letting sits around €12,000-15,000, paid back in 1-2 seasons with 70% occupancy.',
  preciosCta: 'See full pricing table',
  preciosCtaHref: '/en/precios-pladur-menorca',
  preciosCards: [
    { servicio: 'Basic partition', desde: 45, unidad: '€/m²' },
    { servicio: 'Acoustic partition', desde: 52, unidad: '€/m²' },
    { servicio: 'Continuous false ceiling', desde: 29, unidad: '€/m²' },
    { servicio: 'False ceiling with lighting', desde: 35, unidad: '€/m²' },
    { servicio: 'Thermal wall lining', desde: 35, unidad: '€/m²' },
    { servicio: 'Full flat renovation', desde: 10000, unidad: '€ approx.' },
  ],
  preciosDesde: 'From',
  preciosNote: 'Indicative 2026 interior drywall renovation prices in Menorca. VAT not included. Exact price set after an on-site visit and fixed itemised quote in 24-48h.',
  articulos: [
    { slug: 'reforma-integral-piso-menorca-2026', titulo: 'Full flat renovation in Menorca', descripcion: 'Step-by-step guide to a full drywall renovation in Menorca. Timelines, costs and tips.' },
    { slug: 'ventajas-reforma-pladur-menorca', titulo: 'Benefits of renovating with drywall', descripcion: 'Why drywall is ideal for interior renovations: speed, cleanliness and cost savings.' },
    { slug: 'licencia-obra-pladur-menorca', titulo: 'Do you need a building permit for drywall?', descripcion: 'Everything about permits and licences for drywall installation in Menorca.' },
  ],
  faqTitle: 'Drywall renovation FAQs',
  faqSubtitle: 'Answers to the most common questions about interior drywall renovations in Menorca.',
  ctaFinalTitulo: 'Ready to renovate with drywall?',
  ctaFinalSubtitulo: 'On-site technical visit across Menorca. Fixed itemised quote in 24-48h. 1-year warranty on labour.',
  localeBtag: 'en-GB',
} : {
  srOnly: 'Pladur Menorca — reformas interiores con pladur en Menorca. Redistribución de espacios, falsos techos, aislamiento y acabados. +6.000 proyectos completados. Tel: 627 829 723.',
  breadcrumbHome: 'Inicio',
